  "text": "A gradient descent method in the log-Euclidean framework was outlined in [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] for the log-Euclidean elasticity. Here we use the general philosophy described in those references. However, a major added complication is that our method requires two consecutive registrations, from A to B and from B to i.",
